               <provenance>The name Gabra ʾAṣbaha is inserted in the
                     space left for rubrication in the supplication formulas in a crude secondary
                     hand in blue ballpoint pen on 75rb, 76vb. An
                     abbreviated form appears, e.g., on 3rb, 45vb,
                     57rb, 57va.</provenance></history>
